{"tid":886562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：乘客鬧「廢人」車長爆粗反擊","createTime":"2018-11-02T07:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T09:13:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d70650e3dcd8cae15371cab28b4387d7c75ae140","tid":886562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181102/20536467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536467&d=GYl73YhBVON%2FOHT4Pr8dOTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=719419c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536467&h=0b19e9d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181102/20536467</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月02日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：乘客鬧「廢人」車長爆粗反擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181102/large/a1703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181102%2Flarge%2Fa1703a.gif&h=6c94eeb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城巴車長（小圖）與乘客口角，其間不停爆粗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期日晚9點幾，周先生行去中環干諾道中怡和大廈對開巴士站等巴士，見到有架去小西灣藍灣半島嘅城巴788號線停咗喺巴士站，打開咗門傳出鬧交聲。<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到車長同一個男乘客嘈交，個乘客鬧車長「食屎」，戴住口罩嘅車長就不斷爆粗回敬，有乘客上去勸佢哋，但車長好好火氣，堅持唔開車。有乘客埋怨畀咗錢咁點，車長只係叫佢哋等第二班車。周先生話聽到有乘客話驚車長同乘客嘈完交，有可能影響情緒，坐佢車都怕怕，寧願落車。<br />\n<br />\n同車長嘈交嘅男乘客同行女親友鬧車長：「做司機做到你咁！」車長即刻還口：「阿嬸，乜X嘢呀！」男乘客話唔使同呢啲廢人講嘢，車長繼續爆粗：「X家鏟&hellip;&hellip;等差人嚟啦&hellip;&hellip;投訴啦！」周先生覺得車長雖然可能俾乘客侮辱，但都唔應該講粗口，「好似爛仔咁，過份咗，始終佢都係開緊工。」<br />\n<br />\n788號線行走上環港澳碼頭至小西灣藍灣半島，事發時係開去小西灣方向。城巴發言人稱公司關注事件，會作出調查。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：前臂控軚盤雙手撳電話20分鐘　皇崗巴司機玩命"},{"pid":"01c5e6736b99938f1edb0077991f3d728c568a41","tid":886562,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"點解咁多痴線想自殺"},{"pid":"abd0b8b37d7732761180d3340394c5d42122d990","tid":886562,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"245002fc182180a620e4fcb5a79e774da388719b","tid":886562,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"果頭會否衝落海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd73b9763eac1fdbc8a340d09ae9731fd59f1c4a","tid":886562,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"abd0b8b37d7732761180d3340394c5d42122d990","tid":886562,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"通常都係個客問題<br />\n個司機無啦啦點會挑是非"},{"pid":"00d4dd16307fdf8f4561c64da87fda109521bbc6","tid":886562,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"最仆街係花生友<br />\n話緊你呀男乘客同周先生"},{"pid":"ceb7026f180a73c2abe26c40a824542939695b17","tid":886562,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"沖落橋啦"},{"pid":"8e7bf4ba642b9e8d00b0d75d994b7202554f5f82","tid":886562,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d4dd16307fdf8f4561c64da87fda109521bbc6","tid":886562,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"最仆街係花生友<br />\n話緊你呀男乘客同周先生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"啊周生番緊工果陣應該帶個女出黎比人屌啦<br />\n話曬番緊工呀MA"},{"pid":"cd497467a5f5437eee58a4dc80c11698f7ff9824","tid":886562,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"果頭大陸先有單車毀人亡 因為個乘客搞鳩司機"},{"pid":"39aadba2c99b6159cfa5f31e62a38bfdfbf35472","tid":886562,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd497467a5f5437eee58a4dc80c11698f7ff9824","tid":886562,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"